GREETINGS
---------

this repository holds a collection of software to generate audio. the audio was
conceived for use in a wireless communication device, but could be used
anywhere for any purpose.

ppp: Perceptible Phone Programming
rrr: Random-like Ring-tone Realization
ttt: Text Transmission Tones

to make noise, you'll need
- perl
- csound


FILES
-----
gpl.txt : free software license
ppp.txt : explanations, excuses, errata
README : this
rrr.ogg : sample output
rrr.pl :  generator
rrr.tmpl : template for unifiedCSD
ttt.ogg : lather
ttt.pl : rinse
ttt.tmpl : repeat

